<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/ColorPalette> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A structured set of colors associated through recurrent co-occurrence, design conventions, or perceptual harmony, often contributing to the visual identity of an aesthetic."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasMotif> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ассоциирует произведение искусства с узнаваемым повторяющимся мотивом, который в нем присутствует."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Painting> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "表面に絵の具を使って制作された視覚的作品。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Color> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A visual attribute perceived through light, often contributing to aesthetic identity."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasLocationOfOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Location> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/isMemberOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Collega un'entità alla Collezione di cui è membro costituente."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/PrimaryRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Primary Role"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/atTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Указывает временной интервал, в течение которого роль (TimeIndexedRole) является действительной."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "美学"@ja .
