<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/relatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A general symmetric relation indicating that an Aesthetic is related to another entity in some culturally relevant way. Serves as a superproperty for more specific relation types."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasIconicFigure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Associeert een esthetiek met een agent die wordt beschouwd als een emblematische of iconische vertegenwoordiger ervan."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/associationDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Classifica il tipo di associazione codificata da una RepresentativeAssociation. I valori attesi sono gli individui: motifDimension, themeDimension, valueDimension, colorDimension, platformDimension, musicDimension, fashionDimension, iconicFigureDimension."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasRelatedWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "美学と、それを代表するまたはテーマ的に関連すると見なされる作品を関連付ける。"@ja .
