<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/PrimaryRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Role> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasCreator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Verbindt een esthetiek met de agent die deze heeft gecreëerd of aan wie het zijn oorsprong ontleent."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasOriginPeriod> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Указывает временной интервал, в течение которого эстетика появилась впервые."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/themeDimension> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasTheme> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ассоциирует произведение с темой, которую оно выражает или выдвигает на первый план."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasColorPalette> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Associeert een esthetiek met een karakteristiek kleurenpalet dat bijdraagt aan de visuele identiteit."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/representativenessType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "representativeness type"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Beauty> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Красота и уход"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A culturally emergent, open-ended category that groups a collection of heterogeneous elements (e.g., images, colors, objects, sounds, texts) perceived as coherently expressing a recognizable style, affect, or orientation. It is not defined by necessary and sufficient conditions, but by shared associations and family resemblances established by a community. E.g, the Frutiger Aero aesthetic groups glossy textures, bright gradients, nature imagery, and optimistic future cues into a recognizable early-2000s style."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/relatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "美学が文化的に関連する方法で別のエンティティと関連することを示す一般的な対称関係。より具体的な関係タイプのスーパープロパティとして機能する。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/influencedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Связывает эстетику с другой эстетикой, которая послужила источником стилистического, тематического или культурного влияния."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Associeert een esthetiek met een abstracte waarde die de oriëntatie ervan kenmerkt."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/associationDimension> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/ColorPalette> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een gestructureerde set kleuren die verbonden zijn door herhaaldelijke co-occurrentie, ontwerpconventies of perceptuele harmonie, en die vaak bijdragen aan de visuele identiteit van een esthetiek."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Role> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een rol is een contextafhankelijke functie of kwalificatie die aan een entiteit binnen een relatie is toegewezen."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Эстетика"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/ArtistRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "芸術制作の創造者または貢献者としてエージェントが担う役割。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/DigitalPlace> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Digital Place"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasOriginPeriod> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Specifies the time interval during which an Aesthetic first emerged."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Agent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Actor"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/withEntity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Brand> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An identifiable commercial or institutional entity characterized by a name, identity, and set of associated meanings, values, and design practices, which can produce or influence artifacts, styles, and aesthetic associations."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/withEntity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "対象エンティティ"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/representativenessType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tipo di rappresentatività"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasMotif> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "モチーフ"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/RepresentativeAssociation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Associazione rappresentativa"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasMember> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Collega una Collezione a una delle entità che la costituiscono. L'appartenenza non implica esaustività né necessità."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Motif> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Anime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Anime"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/withEntity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a RepresentativeAssociation to the entity that is considered representative of the Aesthetic."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/City> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een stedelijke locatie die wordt gekenmerkt door een dichte bevolking en een gestructureerde infrastructuur."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasSubgenre> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/isSubgenreOf> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasPeriodDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "heeft periodedefinitie"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasPlatform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Platform> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Fashion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "衣服、スタイリング、装飾といった身体的・物質的な表現領域。文化的な意味合いやアイデンティティ、美的方向性を伝達する手段として機能する。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Platform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Социотехническая система, которая обеспечивает и одновременно ограничивает взаимодействие, создание и распространение контента. Она проявляет субъектность через свой дизайн, управление и алгоритмические механизмы, тем самым формируя возникновение и видимость эстетик."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/valueDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "価値観の次元"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/ArchitecturalWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Architectural Work"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/themeDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "theme dimension"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/forAesthetic> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/RepresentativeAssociation> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Fashion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Moda"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/ArchitecturalWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een kunstwerk bestaande uit gebouwen of ruimtelijke structuren ontworpen binnen de architectuur."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasRelatedWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ассоциирует эстетику с произведением, которое считается репрезентативным для неё или тематически связано с ней."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Онтология для моделирования эстетики как эмерджентных, коллекционно-обусловленных категорий, основанных на репрезентативных ассоциациях."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasPlatform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "heeft platform"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/withEntity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "with entity"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Location> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Location"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasIconicFigure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Associa un'Estetica a un Agente considerato suo rappresentante emblematico."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasTheme> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Associates an Artwork with a Theme it conveys, expresses, or foregrounds."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Color> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Color"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/timeInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Collega una PeriodDefinition all'intervallo temporale che essa definisce."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/IconicFigure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Iconic Figure"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/influencedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Group> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Groep"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Motif> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Повторяющийся и узнаваемый элемент (визуальный, концептуальный или стилистический), который формирует идентичность эстетики через многократные ассоциации. Например, мотивы эстетики Frutiger Aero включают скевоморфизм, глянцевые текстуры, пузырьки, образы природы и шрифты семейства Frutiger."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/associationDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/RepresentativeAssociation> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Song> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Lied"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#imports> <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/overlapsWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/relatedTo> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasOriginPeriod> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Specifica l'intervallo temporale durante il quale un'Estetica è emersa per la prima volta."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/influencedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "influenzato da"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasLocation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "ha luogo"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/InteriorDesign> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Дизайн интерьера"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/associationDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "関連性のレベルを分類するための属性。モチーフ、テーマ、価値観、色彩、プラットフォーム、音楽、ファッション、象徴的人物といった各次元を指定する。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasIconicFigure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has iconic figure"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Activity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Активность"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Collection> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un insieme di entità raggruppate assieme, in modo esplicito o implicito, per coerenza percepita o associazioni condivise. Le collezioni costituiscono il mezzo primario tramite il quale le estetiche vengono espresse o riconosciute; non richiedono la fissità o l'esausività dei loro membri."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Agent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Agent"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/LiteraryWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un’opera testuale come romanzi, poesie o narrazioni scritte."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/alternateName> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "альтернативное название"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasPrimaryPlatform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "主要プラットフォーム"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/ArtistRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Artist Role"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasRelatedWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "ha opera associata"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "heeft waarde"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Location> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Locatie"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/endYear> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "год окончания"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TVShow> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Serie TV"@it .
