<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasLocationOfOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TimeInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Tijdsinterval"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/name> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "名称"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/endYear> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "終了年"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Motif> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "美学のアイデンティティ形成に寄与する、特徴的な要素（視覚、概念、スタイル）。繰り返しその美学との関連性として現れる。　例：Frutiger Aeroにおける光沢感、泡、自然のイメージ、Frutiger系フォントなど。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Beauty> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ambito che comprende prodotti, pratiche e industrie legate alla cura della persona, alla cosmetica, alla skincare e all’aspetto corporeo, spesso associato all’espressione estetica e alla costruzione dell’identiteit."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasIconicFigure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/source> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Indicates the Agent from which a PeriodDefinition derives its evidence or authority."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Color> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "光を通じて知覚される視覚的属性。美的アイデンティティに貢献することが多い。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/influenced> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Country> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Land"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasPeriodDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "エンティティと、それを時間的文脈に位置づける期間定義を関連付ける。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/City> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Stad"@nl .
