<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/name> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasMotif> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "ha motivo"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/MusicWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An artwork expressed through sound and musical composition."@en .
