<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Theme> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "美学の根底にある抽象的な概念的方向性またはナラティブ。主要な意味合い、感情的トーンや世界観を捉える。例：Frutiger Aeroの美学のテーマは、楽観的で清潔で自然と統合された近未来のビジョンであると表現できる。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/colorDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "色の次元"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/overlapsWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Indicates that two Aesthetics share significant elements or associations without either being a subgenre of the other. This property is symmetric."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/associatedSubculture> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Koppelt een esthetiek aan een subcultuur die er sociaal mee geassocieerd is of heeft bijgedragen aan het ontstaan en de stabilisatie ervan."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has value"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TVShow> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Artwork> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/MusicWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Opera musicale"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Theme> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un orientamento concettuale astratto o una struttura narrativa sottostante a un’estetica, che ne cattura i significati dominanti, il tono affettivo o la visione del mondo. Ad esempio, il tema dell’estetica Frutiger Aero può essere descritto come una visione ottimistica, pulita e integrata con la natura del futuro prossimo."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/timeInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "time interval"@en .
