<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Region> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "地理的区域。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasSubgenre> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "美学と、その派生系統を構成する、より具体的な美学を関連付ける。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/RepresentativeAssociation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Representative Association"@en .
