<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasPlatform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Associa un'Estetica a una Piattaforma su cui essa circola o è stata diffusa."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Film> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Film"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Collection> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Collection> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "美学とその象徴的な表象との結びつきを基盤とし、多様な要素のコレクションから立ち現れる美学的系統をモデル化するためのオントロジー。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/ArtistRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Kunstenaarsrol"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/source> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Indica l'Agente da cui una PeriodDefinition trae la propria evidenza o autorità."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasLocationOfOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/DigitalPlace> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een virtuele omgeving waar interacties, contentcreatie of gemeenschapspraktijken plaatsvinden (bijv. forums, websites, sociale netwerken)."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasSubgenre> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates an Aesthetic to a more specific Aesthetic that constitutes one of its subvariants."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/ColorPalette> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Цветовая палитра"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/City> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Platform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A socio-technical system that enables and constrains interaction, content production, and dissemination, while exerting agency through its design, governance, and algorithmic mechanisms, thereby shaping the emergence and visibility of aesthetics."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasLocationOfOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "heeft locatie van oorsprong"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/follows> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "follows"@en .
