<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/withRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Film> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "映画"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/iconicFigureDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "измерение иконической фигуры"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Beauty> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Beauty"@en .
