<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/City> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Location> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Role> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un ruolo è una funzione o qualificazione dipendente dal contesto assegnata a un’entità all’interno di una relazione."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/MusicWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Музыкальное произведение"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Person> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un individuo umano."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasLocationOfOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "発祥地"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasPrimaryPlatform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "имеет основную платформу"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/MusicWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un’opera espressa attraverso il suono e la composizione musicale."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/coinedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Collega un'Estetica all'Agente che l'ha coniata o che vi ha dato il nome per la prima volta."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/forAesthetic> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "voor esthetiek"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/associationDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Классифицирует тип ассоциации. Ожидаемые значения — индивиды: измерение мотива (motifDimension), темы (themeDimension), ценности (valueDimension), цвета (colorDimension), платформы (platformDimension), музыки (musicDimension), моды (fashionDimension) или иконической фигуры (iconicFigureDimension)."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/isRoleInTimeOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "TimeIndexedRoleと、その時間的に位置づけられた役割が記述されるプラットフォームを結びつける。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/isSubgenreOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is subgenre of"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/platformDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "dimensione della piattaforma"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/ArchitecturalWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "建築の実践の中でデザインされた建物または空間構造からなる作品。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/alternateName> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "別名"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Fashion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Mode"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Song> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "楽曲"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Brand> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Merk"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Fashion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "ファッション"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/relatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "gerelateerd aan"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/alternateName> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasIconicFigure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "имеет иконическую фигуру"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasOriginPeriod> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "発祥期"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasPlatform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Theme> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Тема"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasMember> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Verbindt een collectie met een van de samenstellende entiteiten. Lidmaatschap impliceert geen volledigheid of strikte noodzaak."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Subculture> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "独自の慣習や価値観、象徴体系を共有し、主流文化とは区別される社会的グループ。特定の美学の創発と定着を促す基盤となることがある。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/MusicWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een kunstwerk uitgedrukt via geluid en muzikale compositie."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/associatedSubculture> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasPlatform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "ha piattaforma"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Theme> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An abstract conceptual orientation or narrative underlying an aesthetic, capturing its dominant meanings, affective tone, or worldview. E.g., the theme of the Frutiger Aero aesthetic can be described as an optimistic, clean, and nature-integrated vision of the near future."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TimeIndexedRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> _:nbc328454a6834b8880aa9e48c2b95d30b11 .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Anime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Форма анимационного искусства, зародившаяся преимущественно в контексте японских медиа."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/RepresentativeAssociation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Representatieve associatie"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/IconicFigure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un ruolo che rappresenta un individuo fortemente associato a un’estetica."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/name> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "naam"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/IconicFigure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "美学と強く関連する個人を表す役割。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/associationDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "association dimension"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/overlapsWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/overlapsWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Geeft aan dat twee esthetieken significante elementen of associaties delen, zonder dat de een een subgenre van de ander is. Deze eigenschap is symmetrisch."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Painting> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "絵画"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/isMemberOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "è membro di"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/FoodItem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een eetbaar item dat esthetische of culturele betekenis kan hebben."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/PeriodDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "期間定義"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/ArtistRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Роль, которую исполняет агент как создатель или участник процесса художественного производства."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/follows> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/isMemberOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is lid van"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Fashion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Сфера телесного и материального самовыражения, включающая одежду, стайлинг и практики украшения тела, посредством которых транслируются культурные смыслы, идентичности и эстетические ориентиры."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasLocation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Associa qualsiasi entità a una collocazione spaziale, fisica o digitale."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TVShow> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A serial audiovisual work produced for television or streaming platforms."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/URL> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Video> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "動画"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/timeInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "期間定義と、それが定義する時間区間を結びつける。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/LiteraryWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een tekstueel kunstwerk zoals een roman, gedicht of geschreven verhaal."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/RepresentativeAssociation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Una relazione reificata che collega un’Estetica a un’entità considerata rappresentativa di essa. Tali associazioni codificano i meccanismi attraverso cui un’estetica viene riconosciuta e costruita, e possono essere qualificate rispetto all’estensione temporale, al grado di rappresentatività o al ruolo (ad esempio, primario)."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/follows> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "volgt"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/InteriorDesign> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Interior Design"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Painting> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een visueel kunstwerk gemaakt met verf op een oppervlak."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasRelatedBrand> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/relatedTo> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasPlatform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/relatedTo> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Film> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Film"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/forAesthetic> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a RepresentativeAssociation to the Aesthetic it qualifies."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/URL> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "URL"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasColorPalette> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has color palette"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasRelatedBrand> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Brand> .
