<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/influencedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "影響を受けた"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/isMemberOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "является элементом"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasPlatform> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TimeInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "時間区間"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/endYear> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "end year"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Video> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "通常デジタルの動画作品。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Videogame> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "視覚的、物語的、ゲームプレイの要素を組み合わせたインタラクティブなデジタル作品。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasLocationOfOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Specifica la collocazione geografica o digitale in cui un'Estetica ha avuto origine."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/follows> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Indicates that one Aesthetic temporally or stylistically follows another. This property is transitive."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Motif> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Мотив"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/LiteraryWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "文学作品"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/isSubgenreOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/colorDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "цветовое измерение"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Brand> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Бренд"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Album> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/MusicWork> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/City> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "密な人口と整備されたインフラを特徴とする都市的場所。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Album> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Альбом"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/isRoleInTimeOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "時間的役割の対象"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/source> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "fonte"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/withRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "met rol"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/representativenessType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TimeIndexedRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A contextual role assigned to an entity within a relation that is explicitly bound to a temporal interval, allowing the same entity to hold different roles at different times."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/PrimaryRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Основная роль"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/isMemberOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing> .
<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Film> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A moving-image artwork produced within cinematic media."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Anime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een vorm van geanimeerd kunstwerk die voornamelijk voortkomt uit Japanse mediacontexten."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Brand> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un’entità commerciale o istituzionale identificabile caratterizzata da un nome, un’identità e un set di significati, valori e pratiche di design associate, che possono produrre o influenzare artefatti, stili e associazioni estetiche."@it .
_:nbc328454a6834b8880aa9e48c2b95d30b10 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TVShow> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "テレビまたはストリーミングプラットフォーム向けに制作された連続的な視聴覚作品。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasPrimaryPlatform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasPlatform> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasMember> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasCreator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "ha creatore"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Value> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "エンティティや美学に関連する抽象的な原理、感情的・価値論的方向性、または評価的次元（倫理的、文化的、美的、またはイデオロギー的）。道徳的判断にのみならず、より広い態度や概念的なスタンスを含む。。例：Frutiger Aeroの美学は楽観主義、清潔さ、テクノ的自然調和といった価値観と関連している。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasOriginPeriod> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Specificeert het tijdsinterval waarin een esthetiek voor het eerst naar voren kwam."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/follows> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Geeft aan dat een esthetiek een andere temporeel of stylistisch volgt. Deze eigenschap is transitief."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/overlapsWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "二つの美学が、どちらも相手のサブジャンルではなく、重要な要素や関連を共有することを示す。この性質は対称的である。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Brand> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "名称、アイデンティティ、特有の価値観やデザイン指針によって識別される商業的・組織的実体。あらゆる品物やスタイルの創出、および美学との関連性の形成に影響を与える。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/URL> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "URL-адрес"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasMotif> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Associeert een kunstwerk met een terugkerend en herkenbaar motief dat het vertoont."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/precedes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Indica che un'Estetica precede temporalmente o stilisticamente un'altra. Questa proprietà è transitiva."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/associatedSubculture> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Collega un'Estetica a una Sottocultura che le è socialmente associata o ha contribuito alla sua emergenza e stabilizzazione."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Video> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Видео"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasRelatedWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Associates an Aesthetic with an Artwork considered representative of or thematically related to it."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Color> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een visueel kenmerk waargenomen door licht, dat vaak bijdraagt aan esthetische identiteit."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Beauty> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Region> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Location> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TimeIndexedRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un ruolo assegnato a un’entità all’interno di una relazione, esplicitamente vincolato a un intervallo temporale, cosa che permette alla stessa entità di avere ruoli diversi in tempi diversi."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/ArchitecturalWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An artwork consisting of buildings or spatial structures designed within architectural practice."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/ArchitecturalWork> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/withRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Определяет Роль, которую сущность играет в рамках отношения временной роли (TimeIndexedRole)."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/motifDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "motif dimension"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Subculture> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A socially situated group or network characterized by shared practices, values, and symbolic systems that differentiate it from broader cultural contexts, often contributing to the emergence and stabilization of specific aesthetics."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasCreator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has creator"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Country> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Геополитическая локация, представляющая собой нацию или государство."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasCreator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Связывает эстетику с агентом, который создал её или способствовал её появлению."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Subculture> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Субкультура"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Group> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een verzameling actoren die handelen of worden geïdentificeerd als een eenheid."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/source> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "期間定義（PeriodDefinition）の根拠、あるいは権威的な裏付けとなるエージェント（出典元）を示す。  "@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/isMemberOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/PeriodDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een temporeel begrensd maar potentieel onvolledig interval dat wordt gebruikt om entiteiten of verschijnselen in de tijd te plaatsen, waarbij vage of overlappende grenzen mogelijk zijn, in overeenstemming met modellen zoals PeriodO."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/isSubgenreOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "è sottogenere di"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Painting> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un’opera visiva realizzata con pittura su una superficie."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasSubgenre> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/name> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "nome"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Brand> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Идентифицируемая коммерческая или общественная организация, характеризующаяся названием, идентичностью и набором смыслов, ценностей и практик дизайна, которая может создавать или влиять на артефакты, стили и эстетические ассоциации."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/relatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#SymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TimeIndexedRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Tijdgeïndexeerde rol"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Image> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Platform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un sistema socio-tecnico che abilita e al tempo stesso vincola l’interazione, la produzione di contenuti e la loro diffusione, esercitando un’agenzia attraverso il proprio design, le forme di governance e i meccanismi algoritmici, e contribuendo così a modellare l’emergere e la visibilità delle estetiche."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Song> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Canzone"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/atTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Specificeert het tijdsinterval waarin een TimeIndexedRole geldig is."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasRelatedWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "имеет ассоциирующееся произведение"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasPeriodDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "ha definizione di periodo"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasColorPalette> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
