<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Subculture> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een sociaal gesitueerde groep of netwerk gekenmerkt door gedeelde praktijken, waarden en symbolische systemen die het onderscheiden van bredere culturele contexten, en vaak bijdragen aan het ontstaan en de stabilisatie van specifieke esthetiek."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Videogame> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Видеоигра"@ru .
_:nbc328454a6834b8880aa9e48c2b95d30b11 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/motifDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "モチーフの次元"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Platform> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#InformationEntity> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/PrimaryRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "主要役割"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/overlapsWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "overlapt met"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/alternateName> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "alternate name"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasColorPalette> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "heeft kleurenpalet"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Person> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Person"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasLocationOfOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Указывает географическое или цифровое местоположение, в котором эстетика возникла впервые."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/influenced> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Связывает эстетику с другой эстетикой, на которую она оказала влияние (в стиле, мотивах, ценностях и т. д.)."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Fashion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un ambito di espressione materiale che coinvolge abbigliamento e pratiche di stile, attraverso cui si comunicano significati culturali, identità e orientamenti estetici."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TVShow> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un’opera audiovisiva seriale prodotta per televisione o piattaforme streaming."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/PrimaryRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een rol die een primaire of centrale associatie binnen een context aangeeft."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/influencedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/forAesthetic> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Ontologia per modellare le estetiche come categorie emergenti basate su collezioni e associazioni rappresentative."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/forAesthetic> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Collega una AssociazioneRappresentativa all'Estetica che essa qualifica."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/ColorPalette> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Palette di colori"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/associationDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Classifies the kind of association. Expected values are the named individuals: motifDimension, themeDimension, valueDimension, colorDimension, platformDimension, musicDimension, fashionDimension, iconicFigureDimension."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Video> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A moving-image artwork, typically digital."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/influencedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "beïnvloed door"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasMotif> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Motif> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/timeInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TimeInterval> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Painting> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Dipinto"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Agent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Сущность, способная действовать, создавать или влиять на культурные артефакты или эстетику, включая индивидов и группы."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Esthetiek"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Anime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "アニメ"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/InteriorDesign> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Interieurontwerp"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "ha valore"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasOriginPeriod> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TimeInterval> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/withRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Specifies the Role held by the entity within a TimeIndexedRole relation."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Aesthetic> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Una categoria culturalmente emergente e aperta che raggruppa una collezione di elementi eterogenei (ad esempio immagini, colori, oggetti, suoni, testi) percepiti come espressione coerente di uno stile, un’affettività o un orientamento riconoscibile. Non è definita da condizioni necessarie e sufficienti, ma da associazioni condivise e somiglianze di famiglia stabilite da una comunità. Ad esempio, l’estetica Frutiger Aero raggruppa texture lucide, gradienti brillanti, immagini della natura e richiami a un futuro ottimistico in uno stile riconoscibile dei primi anni 2000."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Value> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "価値観"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/atTime> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Specifica l'intervallo temporale durante il quale un TimeIndexedRole è valido."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TimeIndexedRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Контекстная роль, присваиваемая сущности в рамках отношения, которое явно привязано к временному интервалу, что позволяет одной и той же сущности выполнять разные роли в разное время."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/URL> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "URL"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TVShow> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Сериал"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Region> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "地域"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasPeriodDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Associates an entity with a PeriodDefinition that situates it within a temporal context."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Collection> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Коллекция"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/associatedSubculture> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Связывает эстетику с субкультурой, которая ассоциируется с ней в обществе или способствовала её возникновению и стабилизации."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasRelatedBrand> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "ha brand associato"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Subculture> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Социально локализованная группа или сеть, характеризующаяся общими практиками, ценностями и символическими системами, которые отличают её от более широкого культурного контекста; часто способствует возникновению и стабилизации определенных эстетик."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "\"Version 1.1 with alignments to DOLCE\"" .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/influencedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/relatedTo> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasMember> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "имеет участника/элемент"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "価値観"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Value> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An abstract principle, an affective/axiological orientation, or evaluative dimension (ethical, cultural, aesthetic, or ideological) associated with entities or aesthetics. Values are not limited to moral judgments but include broader attitudinal or conceptual stances. E.g., the aesthetic Frutiger Aero is associated with optimism, cleanliness, techno-natural harmony."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasLocationOfOrigin> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "место происхождения"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/IconicFigure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een rol die een individu vertegenwoordigt dat sterk geassocieerd wordt met een esthetiek."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Platform> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Song> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een enkele muzikale compositie, meestal bestaande uit tekst en melodie."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/alternateName> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "alternatieve naam"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Activity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Action> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Fashion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#InformationEntity> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/RepresentativeAssociation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A reified relation linking an Aesthetic to an entity that is considered representative of it. Such associations encode the mechanisms through which an aesthetic is recognized and constructed, and may be qualified by temporal scope, degree of representativeness, or role (e.g., primary)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Film> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Film"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/influenced> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Collega un'Estetica a un'altra Estetica che essa ha influenzato in termini di stile, motivi o valori, o altro."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/withRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TimeIndexedRole> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Brand> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/fashionDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "mode dimensie"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Video> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Video"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/iconicFigureDimension> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "iconic figure dimension"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/forAesthetic> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "象徴的な関連（Representative Association）が、どの美学的系統を規定・説明しているかを示す。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Vibe Ontology"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Activity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Attività"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "美学と、その方向性を特徴づける抽象的な価値観を関連付ける。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Video> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een kunstwerk van bewegende beelden, meestal digitaal."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/representativenessType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/RepresentativeAssociation> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/DigitalPlace> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Group> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "一つの単位として行動または識別されるエージェントの集合。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasLocation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Associates any entity with a physical or digital spatial location."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TimeIndexedRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/TimeInterval> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Временной отрезок с началом и/или концом, который может быть точно определенным или приблизительным; используется для квалификации временной валидности сущностей, ролей или ассоциаций."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Collection> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A set of entities grouped together, either explicitly or implicitly, based on perceived coherence, curation, or shared associations. Collections function as the primary means through which an Aesthetic is expressed and recognized, without requiring fixed or exhaustive membership."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasCreator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Collega un'Estetica all'Agente che l'ha creata o a cui essa deve la propria origine."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/timeInterval> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Theme> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Een abstracte conceptuele oriëntatie of narratief dat ten grondslag ligt aan een esthetiek en de dominante betekenissen, affectieve toon of wereldbeeld vastlegt. Bijv. het thema van de Frutiger Aero-esthetiek kan worden beschreven als een optimistische, schone en in de natuur geïntegreerde visie op de nabije toekomst."@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/IconicFigure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Role> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/City> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An urban location characterised by dense population and structured infrastructure."@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Agent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Агент"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasRelatedWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Artwork> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Person> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "個々の人間エージェント。"@ja .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/hasLocation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has location"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Region> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un'area geografica."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Artwork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Opera d'arte"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/InteriorDesign> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Форма архитектурной работы, ориентированная на проектирование внутренних пространств."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Fashion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Мода"@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Role> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Роль — это зависящая от контекста функция или квалификация, присваиваемая сущности в рамках отношения."@ru .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/coinedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "coniato da"@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Album> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Album"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/source> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "bron"@nl .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/ColorPalette> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Quality> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Image> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Image"@en .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/PeriodDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un intervallo temporale delimitato ma potenzialmente impreciso usato per collocare entità o fenomeni nel tempo, che consente di definire confini vaghi o con sovrapposizioni, allineato a modellazioni come PeriodO."@it .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Fashion> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/ArchitecturalWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Artwork> .
